      "suggested_fix": "Add Go code blocks for `ResolvedSoul`, `SoulSnapshot`, the parser entry point (`ParseSoul(ctx, path string) (*SoulDef, error)`), the prompt-assembly contract (`AssembleAgentSoulBlock(snapshot SoulSnapshot, budget int) (string, bool)`), and the OpenAPI DTOs (`AgentSoulPayload`, `AgentSoulSectionPayload`) with field-by-field coments. State explicitly which fields are read-only and which are part of the redaction surface."
